Student Record Management System is a simple and user-friendly Python project 💻 developed to manage student details efficiently. This system helps users to ➕ add, 🔍 search, ✏ update, 👀 view, and ❌ delete student records easily through a menu-driven interface.

It reduces manual work 🗂 and keeps student data organized in a digital format 📁. The project is built using Python concepts like 🔁 loops, ⚡ functions, 🤔 conditional statements, 📦 dictionaries, and CRUD operations, making it a great project for improving logical thinking and programming skills 🚀.